OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1774962671
OL,3,CResidents demand action as they say
OL,4,Clandfill stench returns 'with
OL,5,Cvengeance'
OL,7,FComplaints about a foul-smelling odour
OL,8,Flinked to a local landfill site have
OL,9,Fsurged in Wiltshire, with residents
OL,10,Fdescribing a "putrid" stench so
OL,11,Foverwhelming it's making them feel
OL,12,Funwell.
OL,14,FThe Environment Agency (EA) said it
OL,15,Freceived more than 100 complaints in
OL,16,FFebruary about the recurring smell in
OL,17,Fand around Calne - up from 16 in
OL,18,FJanuary.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1774962671
OL,3,CResidents demand action as they say
OL,4,Clandfill stench returns 'with
OL,5,Cvengeance'
OL,7,FThe smell has previously been linked
OL,8,Fto escaping gas from the Lower Compton
OL,9,Flandfill site, operated by Hills Waste
OL,10,FSolutions.
OL,12,FThe company said it's working hard to
OL,13,Fcontain emissions, but Simone Partner,
OL,14,Fwho lives in the area with her partner
OL,15,Fand two-year-old child, told ITV News
OL,16,Fthe impact on their health has become
OL,17,Fimpossible to ignore.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1774962671
OL,3,CResidents demand action as they say
OL,4,Clandfill stench returns 'with
OL,5,Cvengeance'
OL,7,F"It's beyond an odour," she said.
OL,8,F"It's so putrid, it's like having a
OL,9,Fgas leak. It penetrates the house even
OL,10,Fwhen the doors and windows are shut."
OL,12,FShe added: "I personally wake up with
OL,13,Fshortness of breath, I feel sick, I
OL,14,Fget severe headaches, and my two-year-
OL,15,Fold is coughing in the middle of the
OL,16,Fnight. You just can't escape it."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1774962671
OL,3,CResidents demand action as they say
OL,4,Clandfill stench returns 'with
OL,5,Cvengeance'
OL,7,FHer partner, Joe Menghini, said he
OL,8,Fbelieves the smell, which he describes
OL,9,Fas eggy, gassy or stagnant, is being
OL,10,Fdeliberately released after dark,
OL,11,Fthough Hills strongly denied this.
OL,13,FHe explained: "During the day, there's
OL,14,Fno smell, but when it gets dark,
OL,15,Fespecially over the weekend, the smell
OL,16,Fbecomes overbearing."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1774962671
OL,3,CResidents demand action as they say
OL,4,Clandfill stench returns 'with
OL,5,Cvengeance'
OL,7,FResidents hoped the long-running
OL,8,Fproblem had been resolved when the EA
OL,9,Fintervened in June 2025, serving Hills
OL,10,Fwith an enforcement notice ordering
OL,11,Fthe company to complete a programme of
OL,12,Flandfill capping designed to trap
OL,13,Fescaping gas and reduce odours.
OL,15,F"They did some work last summer, but
OL,16,Fit's come back with a vengeance," said
OL,17,FMs Partner. "I don't know when it's
OL,18,Fgoing to stop".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1774962671
OL,3,CResidents demand action as they say
OL,4,Clandfill stench returns 'with
OL,5,Cvengeance'
OL,7,FAnother Calne resident, Leigh Randall,
OL,8,Fsaid he doesn't let his three-year-old
OL,9,Fdaughter play outside "because of what
OL,10,Fit does to her breathing."
OL,12,F"If we could afford to move, we would.
OL,13,FIt's that bad. It's that distressing,"
OL,14,Fhe said.
OL,16,FLiberal Democrat MP for Chippenham,
OL,17,FSarah Gibson, said she has escalated
OL,18,Fthe issue to the Environment
OL,19,FSecretary, Emma Reynolds MP.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1774962671
OL,3,CResidents demand action as they say
OL,4,Clandfill stench returns 'with
OL,5,Cvengeance'
OL,7,FShe said: "I think the Environment
OL,8,FSecretary will be able to put more
OL,9,Fpressure on the Environment Agency to
OL,10,Fput resources into doing something
OL,11,Fabout it.
OL,13,F"Residents are upset because they
OL,14,Fthought something had been done about
OL,15,Fit, and now they find they are back
OL,16,Fwhere they started, and they feel let
OL,17,Fdown."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1774962671
OL,3,CResidents demand action as they say
OL,4,Clandfill stench returns 'with
OL,5,Cvengeance'
OL,7,FIn a statement, Hills said it was
OL,8,F"aware of the rise in complaints" and
OL,9,Fwas "continuing to co-operate fully
OL,10,Fand transparently with EA
OL,11,Finvestigations, ensuring they have
OL,12,Faccess to our site and operations."
OL,14,FThe company added that it is working
OL,15,Fhard to improve operations at the
OL,16,FLower Compton landfill site to help
OL,17,Fcontain fugitive emissions of landfill
OL,18,Fgas, in accordance with its
OL,19,Fenvironmental permit.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1774962671
OL,3,CResidents demand action as they say
OL,4,Clandfill stench returns 'with
OL,5,Cvengeance'
OL,7,F"Where we need to make improvements,
OL,8,Fwe are making them," the company said.
OL,10,FThe Environment Agency added: "We
OL,11,Fsympathise with the Calne community
OL,12,Fand feel that no area should have to
OL,13,Ftolerate unpleasant odours.
OL,15,F"Our officers have been out in Calne
OL,16,Fand the surrounding areas to assess
OL,17,Fconditions and identify all potential
OL,18,Fsources.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
