PN,43310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1774962671
OL,3,CResidents demand action as they say
OL,4,Clandfill stench returns 'with
OL,5,Cvengeance'
OL,7,F"We encourage anyone with information,
OL,8,For who wishes to report concerns about
OL,9,Fthe smell, to contact our 24/7
OL,10,Fincident hotline on 0800 807060."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
